Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.06,0:00:34.16,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}当我闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:38.61,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}一切都是那么令我感到惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:43.01,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}他们的身影又再度清楚浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:47.81,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}活生生出现在我的银幕里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:52.62,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我爱人的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:57.28,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我战斗时的脸孔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:06.61,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}全部都在我的脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:11.79,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我们一天的时间 让我们找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.91,0:01:16.07,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}引领到你世界的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:21.01,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}再给我一个晚上 让你能再看到我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:24.51,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我就会相信这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:28.54,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}回忆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:34.53,op_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,2000)}{\be1}回忆啊...
