Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.28,0:23:47.75,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:51.82,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}已做好觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:55.33,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}将扛起沉重的荣耀
